Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Good afternoon! Thank you for calling Verity Capital. This is Jessica. How can I assist you today?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Hi, Jessica. This is Mark. I'm interested in learning more about your investment portfolios, but I have a few concerns.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Hi Mark, nice to meet you. Id be happy to help. What specific concerns do you have?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Well, I've been burned by high management fees in the past. I'm worried that Ill end up paying more in fees than I actually earn.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: I understand your concern, Mark. At Verity Capital, we pride ourselves on transparency. Our management fees are very competitive, and we have a variety of portfolio options that can fit different financial goals and fee structures. Would you like a detailed breakdown of our fee structure?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Yes, that would be great. Also, Im concerned about the risk factor. I know investing always comes with risks, but Im looking for something that offers a good balance between risk and return.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Absolutely, balancing risk and return is crucial. We offer a range of portfolios from conservative to aggressive. Our financial advisors can work with you to understand your risk tolerance and recommend a portfolio that aligns with your comfort level. Would you be open to setting up a meeting with one of our advisors?

Speaker: Customer
Text: That sounds like a good idea. But Im also wondering how Verity Capitals performance compares to other firms. I've seen mixed reviews online.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: I appreciate your due diligence, Mark. Our portfolios have consistently outperformed the market over the last five years. We can provide you with detailed performance reports as well as client testimonials if you'd like.

Speaker: Customer
Text: Yes, I would like to see those reports and testimonials. One last thing  whats the minimum investment required to get started?

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Our minimum investment starts at $10,000 for most portfolios, but we do have some options that require less. It really depends on what youre aiming to achieve.

Speaker: Customer
Text: Okay, that works for me. What are the next steps?

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Great to hear! Ill email you the fee structure, performance reports, and client testimonials. Then I'll set up a meeting with one of our financial advisors at a time that suits you. How does that sound?

Speaker: Customer
Text: That sounds good, Jessica. Thank you for your help.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: My pleasure, Mark. Ill send the email shortly and follow up to schedule your meeting. Have a great day!
